    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后T10ms这里要做两个检查：5毫秒的幂等性校验走Retail_CustomerLoyalty，8毫秒的JWT验证走Retail_OrderManagement。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T10ms",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "idempotency check",
        "JWT validation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，T10ms到T25ms之间我加上了wallet balance check，12毫秒走Retail_PointOfSale，然后是15毫秒的reserve funds回到Retail_OrderManagement。同步阶段总共40毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "wallet balance check",
        "reserve funds"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来T50ms响应返回给用户，包含10毫秒网络延迟，T60ms用户看到Transaction ID和成功状态，这里要标注Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T50ms",
        "T60ms",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Transaction ID"
